mu (0.9) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Simplified the KNPluginManager.
  * Update the KNJsonDatabase module to 3.0. Support fast data reading.
  * Support clear up the image directory when loading the images.
  * Increase the write data operation maximum bound to 400.
  * Use brand new KNMusicModel module, no more QStandardItemModel.
  * Change the policy to load images from hard disk, optimized the start up speed.
  * Change the policy to parse and find files in music library.
  * Fixed the drag and drop bug in playlist caused by the QTreeView can only drop one data.
  * Fixed the crashed bug caused by use AutoConnection and overflow the call stack in the library. 
  * Fixed the proxy model sort unstable bug.
  * Fixed the library tree view bug.
  * More in NEWS

 -- Saki Tojo <tomguts@126.com> Tue, 11 Oct 2015 11:32:00 +1100

mu (0.8) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New main player UI.
  * New shuffle loop mode.
  * New lyrics download dialog.
  * New preference item cancel button for canceling single option.
  * New Mac OS X tray controls.
  * New Windows taskbar controls for up/down volume, slient and loop mode.
  * Support minimized to tray icon on Windows.
  * Improve UI performance by replaced QOpacityGraphicsEffect to QPainter.
  * Fixed the wrong lyrics information provided bug in TTPod server module.
  * Fixed the mouse penetrate bug in album art mode.

 -- Saki Tojo <tomguts@126.com> Tue, 17 Mar 2015 08:30:00 +0800

mu (0.7) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Improve initial running speed. (Project S)
  * Improve music playing speed. (Project S)
  * Improve lyrics search speed. (Project S)
  * Optimized lyrics download policy. (Project S)
  * Optimized music switch policy. (Project S)
  * Add import files and play current playlist button on playlist panel.
  * Support rename the file for any name. (experimental)
  * Fixed the image update bug.

